<paragraph id="8BEF36930379EF671CEF7865FC996A71" blockId="6.[363,1224,1742,1840]" box="[731,856,1814,1840]" pageId="6" pageNumber="74">
<figureCitation id="136B2A160379EF671CEF7865FC996A71" box="[731,856,1814,1840]" captionStart="Fig" captionStartId="7.[189,232,1892,1918]" captionTargetBox="[221,1385,525,1854]" captionTargetId="figure-110@7.[202,1385,525,1854]" captionTargetPageId="7" captionText="Fig. 3. A–D. Berlandina artaxerxes sp. nov., holotype, ♂ (SMF). A. Habitus, dorsal view. B–D. Palp, ventral, proventral and retrolateral views. –E–G. Berlandina mesopotamica Al-Khazali,2020, ♀ (MHNG). E. Habitus, dorsal view. F–G. Epigyne, ventral and dorsal views. Abbreviations: Ao = apical outgrowth; Eb = embolar base; Po = pointed process. Scale bars: 0.2 mm, unless stated otherwise." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4906013" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/4906013/files/figure.png" pageId="6" pageNumber="74">Fig. 3A–D</figureCitation>
